
'''''Nakom''''' ni filime yikinamico yakozwe mu mwaka wa 2016 iyobowe na Kelly Daniela Norris na TW Pittman .  Iyi filime yagaragaye bwa mbere ku isi mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filime rya 66 rya Berlin mu gice cya Panorama  kandi yatumiriwe kuzerekanwa bwa mbere muri [[Amerika]] y'Amajyaruguru mu iserukiramuco rya new diroctorss i New York. 

